=== 上市前 ===
在發布首支預告片後，[[Polygon|Polygon]]等多家新聞媒體及該系列的粉絲將本作和《[[塞尔达传说_旷野之息|薩爾達傳說 曠野之息]]》進行了比較，並指出兩者有著明顯的相似之處，包含類開放世界的遊戲玩法和藝術風格。但也有許多粉絲對本作的貼圖品質及畫面等問題感到擔憂。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The new open-world Pokémon has Breath of the Wild vibes|url=https://www.polygon.com/2021/2/26/22303035/pokemon-legends-arceus-zelda-breath-of-the-wild-switch|access-date=2022-02-04|date=2021-02-26|last=Diaz|first=Ana|work=Polygon|language=en-US}}</ref>

本作在發售前約一週，在[[YouTube|YouTube]]、[[Twitter|Twitter]]和[[Reddit|Reddit]]等平台已有大量玩家開始遊玩未上市的實體遊戲片<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pokémon Legends: Arceus’ new forms leak, and people have strong Typhlosion opinions|url=https://www.polygon.com/22891556/pokemon-legends-arceus-full-pokedex-leak-new-hisuian-forms|access-date=2022-01-24|date=2022-01-19|last=Carpenter|first=Nicole|work=Polygon|language=en-US}}</ref>、甚至於[[Twitch|Twitch]]直播遊玩畫面，但相關內容並沒有被[[任天堂|任天堂]]和[[寶可夢公司|寶可夢公司]]下架<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pokemon Legends Arceus leak on Twitch, one week before launch|url=https://clutchpoints.com/pokemon-legends-arceus-leak-twitch/|access-date=2022-02-09|date=2022-01-23|last=Irorita|first=Franz Christian|work=ClutchPoints|language=en}}</ref>。

=== 上市後 ===
根據彙總媒體[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]，本作獲得了普遍的好評<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pokemon Legends: Arceus|url=https://www.metacritic.com/game/switch/pokemon-legends-arceus|access-date=2022-02-04|work=Metacritic|language=en}}</ref>。[[The_Verge|The Verge]]稱讚本作大幅改變寶可夢既有固定的玩法。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]則表示很滿意《阿爾宙斯》中新的動畫特效和表現，還表示：「野生的寶可夢比以往的任何遊戲都還更有生命力。」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pokémon Legends: Arceus review - budget bare-minimum, or the series' purest form?|url=https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2022-01-26-pokemon-legends-arceus-review-budget-bare-minimum-or-the-series-purest-form|access-date=2022-02-04|date=2022-01-26|last=Tapsell|first=Chris|work=Eurogamer|language=en}}</ref>[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]則批評了本作的圖形風格以及缺乏的寶可夢，但對於對戰鬥系統和探索感到相當滿意。「當戰鬥結束後，可以直接回到探索或繼續捕捉其他寶可夢，無需像以往等待經驗值的取得或是習得招式。一旦上手後，很容易在潛行、捕捉、戰鬥和探索的節奏中迷失自我。」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pokémon Legends: Arceus is a breath of fresh air for a stale franchise|url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2022/01/pokemon-legends-arceus-is-a-breath-of-fresh-air-for-a-stale-franchise/|access-date=2022-02-04|date=2022-01-26|last=Cunningham|first=Andrew|work=Ars Technica|language=en-us}}</ref>

=== 銷量 ===
本作上市首3天於[[日本|日本]]售出超過142萬套的實體版遊戲，成為[[任天堂Switch|任天堂Switch]]平台上首週銷量第二高的遊戲<ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:『ポケモンレジェンズ アルセウス』発売3日間で142.5万本を販売。スイッチ向けソフトの初週販売本数としては『あつ森』に次ぐ歴代2位 |url=https://www.famitsu.com/news/202202/03250131.html|access-date=2022-02-04|work=ファミ通.com|language=ja}}</ref>。2022年2月4日，[[寶可夢公司|寶可夢公司]]宣布全球上市3天全球銷量已達到650萬套，刷新[[寶可夢系列_(遊戲)|寶可夢系列]]新高紀錄<ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:『ポケモンレジェンズ アルセウス』初週世界販売本数650万本突破 Nintendo Switchのポケモンシリーズとして最速・最多（リアルサウンド）|url=https://news.yahoo.co.jp/articles/2542f1138262efed86bd3afeaa2afff2341d3f8d|access-date=2022-02-04|work=Yahoo!ニュース|language=ja}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Galloway|first1=Ryan|title=Pokémon Legends: Arecus sells over 6.5 million copies in first week|url=https://dotesports.com/pokemon/news/pokemon-legends-arecus-sells-over-6-5-million-copies-in-first-week|access-date=2022-02-04|work=Dot Esports|date=2022-02-04|archive-date=2022-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220204061416/https://dotesports.com/pokemon/news/pokemon-legends-arecus-sells-over-6-5-million-copies-in-first-week|url-status=live|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Skrebels|first1=Joe|title=Pokémon Legends: Arceus Is Selling Faster than Mainline Switch Pokémon Games|url=https://sea.ign.com/pokemon-legends-arceus/181527/news/pokemon-legends-arceus-is-selling-faster-than-mainline-switch-pokemon-games|access-date=2022-02-09|work=IGN|date=2022-02-04|language=en|archive-date=2022-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220209094408/https://sea.ign.com/pokemon-legends-arceus/181527/news/pokemon-legends-arceus-is-selling-faster-than-mainline-switch-pokemon-games|url-status=live}}</ref>。

截至2022年3月31日，本作共於全球售出1264萬套<ref>{{cite news|title=Switch worldwide sales top 107.65 million, Pokemon Legends: Arceus tops 12.64 million|url=https://www.gematsu.com/2022/05/switch-worldwide-sales-top-107-65-million-pokemon-legends-arceus-tops-12-64-million|access-date=2022-05-10|work=Gematsu|date=2022-05-10|language=en}}</ref>。

